OL,3,CSir Sadiq Khan made a peer as Sir Keir
OL,4,CStarmer prepares to leave office
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan is to be made a peer
OL,7,Falong with 25 other new members of the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords as Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fprepares to leave office.
OL,11,FThe Labour London Mayor will take his
OL,12,Fseat on the red benches with former
OL,13,Fcabinet secretary Sir Chris Wormald
OL,14,Fand Sir Brian Leveson, a retired
OL,15,Fsenior judge.
OL,17,FThey appeared on a list of names
OL,18,Fissued by Downing Street to which No
OL,19,F10 said the King has been "graciously
OL,20,Fpleased to signify his intention of
OL,21,Fconferring peerages".
OL,26,@{D@[OU}D@TO]
