OL,3,CSir Sadiq Khan made a peer as Sir Keir
OL,4,CStarmer prepares to leave office
OL,6,FA Government source said: "Sadiq has
OL,7,Fbeen a brilliant mayor who has
OL,8,Ftransformed London for the better, so
OL,9,Fthis is thoroughly deserved.
OL,11,F"He has cut violent crime to record
OL,12,Flows, cleaned up the capital's air,
OL,13,Fdelivered the Elizabeth Line and got
OL,14,FLondon building council homes again."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Mayor of London
OL,17,Fsaid Sir Sadiq Khan was "honoured to
OL,18,Fbe given a peerage".
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@AOUvD@eO]yD@YOUzD@SO]
