OL,3,CSir Sadiq Khan made a peer as Sir Keir
OL,4,CStarmer prepares to leave office
OL,6,FThey added: "London gave Sadiq the
OL,7,Fopportunities to go from a council
OL,8,Festate to being Mayor of London, and
OL,9,Fhis focus will continue to be ensuring
OL,10,Fthat all Londoners get the same shot
OL,11,Fat reaching their full potential that
OL,12,FLondon gave him and his family.
OL,14,F"Serving as mayor of the greatest city
OL,15,Fin the world continues to be the
OL,16,Fprivilege of Sadiq's life.
OL,26,@nD@MOUvD@AOU
