OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784630877
OL,3,CSir Sadiq Khan made a peer as Sir Keir
OL,4,CStarmer prepares to leave office
OL,6,F"He is excited about what more can be
OL,7,Fdelivered in the years ahead and he
OL,8,Fwill devote his time and energy to
OL,9,Fstanding up for our city and building
OL,10,Fa fairer, safer and greener London for
OL,11,Feveryone."
OL,13,FSir Sadiq is not seeking a ministerial
OL,14,Frole, it is understood, and has not
OL,15,Fyet decided whether he will stand for
OL,16,Fanother term as mayor.
